AttributeList.Text: ================================================================================ This module is used inside another FB where one alarm shall be generated when one (security) input becomes True. The alarm can be True only when the input Enable Alarm is also True. The alarm can be True only when the input Disable Alarm is False. When the alarm is disabled from HMI, a boolean output is available to inform the upper level and do action in the Alarm summary. When the conditions to generate the alarm disappear, a boolean output is available to inform the upper level that the alarm can be reset. The alarm is reset by means of the AlarmResetPB signal. ================================================================================
